Description

This package contains the main classes for the Hospital Management System (HMS).

    Description
    AppointmentService
    AppointmentService provides functionalities to manage medical appointments.
  • Classes in org.hms.services.appointment used by org.hms.services.appointment
    Class
    Description
    AppointmentInformation
    Represents the details of a medical appointment, including the appointment ID, patient ID, doctor ID, appointment time slot, and the status of the appointment.
    AppointmentOutcome
    The AppointmentOutcome class represents the outcome of an appointment.
    AppointmentSchedule
    The AppointmentSchedule class is responsible for storing and managing a scheduling matrix which includes information about doctor IDs and their assigned time slots.
    AppointmentStatus
    The AppointmentStatus enum represents the various states an appointment can be in.
    IAppointmentDataInterface
    Interface representing the data management operations for appointments.
